# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# .gitignore - Team Luzin Coursework One
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 
# This .gitignore keeps all source code, documentation, and configuration
# while excluding generated files, secrets, and development artifacts.
#
# COMMITTED (tracked by Git):
#   ✓ modules/           - All source code
#   ✓ test/              - All test files
#   ✓ config/            - Configuration directory (empty template)
#   ✓ static/            - Example outputs and documentation
#   ✓ docs/              - Sphinx documentation source files
#   ✓ *.py files         - All Python scripts
#   ✓ *.md files         - All markdown documentation
#   ✓ *.toml files       - Poetry configuration
#   ✓ *.ini files        - Test and coverage configuration
#   ✓ *.rst files        - Sphinx documentation files
#   ✓ .gitignore         - This file
#
# IGNORED (not tracked):
#   ✗ conf.yaml          - Database credentials (SECRETS)
#   ✗ __pycache__/       - Python compiled bytecode
#   ✗ .pytest_cache/     - Test cache
#   ✗ .coverage          - Coverage reports
#   ✗ htmlcov/           - HTML coverage reports
#   ✗ *.log              - Log files
#   ✗ *.csv              - Generated CSV files
#   ✗ *.parquet          - Generated Parquet files
#   ✗ .venv/             - Virtual environment
#   ✗ poetry.lock        - Dependency lock file
#   ✗ docs/_build/       - Built documentation
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# PYTHON ARTIFACTS
═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python
*.egg-info/
*.egg
MANIFEST
dist/
build/
.eggs/
lib/
lib64/
parts/
sdist/
var/
wheels/
pip-wheel-metadata/
share/python-wheels/
develop-eggs/
downloads/
.installed.cfg

# VIRTUAL ENVIRONMENTS
═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
.venv/
venv/
ENV/
env/
.env

# TEST & COVERAGE
═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
.pytest_cache/
.coverage
.coverage.*
htmlcov/
.tox/
.hypothesis/
test_output.log
nosetests.xml
coverage.xml
.cache

# IDE & EDITOR
═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace

# OS FILES
═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
Thumbs.db

# TEMPORARY FILES
═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
*.tmp
*.bak
*.temp
.~*
*.swp

# CREDENTIALS & SECRETS (NEVER COMMIT)
═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Coursework submission requires config/conf.yaml to exist in the repository.
# Keep only non-sensitive/default values in this file.
!config/conf.yaml
config/secrets/
.env.local
.env.*.local

# LOG FILES
═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
*.log
pipeline.log
calculate_var_all_stocks.log
composite_scoring.log
export_analytics_to_minio.log

# GENERATED DATA & OUTPUTS
═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
analytics/
*.csv
*.parquet
*.xlsx
*.xls
portfolio_*.csv
signals_*.csv
execution_signals_*.csv
momentum_factors_*.parquet
portfolio_*.parquet
selections_*.parquet
selections_*.csv
